		<div class="courseListDescription">Through a combination of lecture and in-studio workshops, students learn foundational skills in digital sound production: recording, editing, and mixing. Students then apply these skills through the creation of soundscapes across a variety of media, including radio, screen, etc., and develop a strong appreciation for the relationship of sound to image and the role of sound in media.</div>
	
	
