		<div class="courseListDescription">This course offers intermediate-level skills in digital content production with a focus on motion graphics, animation, and the web.  The course includes group-critiques, in-class workshops, production exercises and tutorials, and requires students to have a basic familiarity with computers and digital tools.</div>
	
	
