		<div class="courseListDescription">This studio course will examine how emerging wearable technologies such as e-textiles and smart materials are influencing the landscape of creative inquiry. From cyborgs and space travel to fashion and fitness, students will explore creating body-centric technologies that extend and augment the human form.</div>
	
	
