		<div class="courseListDescription">This course will explore the rapidly expanding world of eSports. By way of lectures, students will examine different elements of eSports, such as culture, multi-platform streaming, gaming development, gaming theory, online communities and the impact of eSports by and via media. eSports will emphasize the impact of the globalization and commercialization of eSports on the traditional broadcast industry.</div>
	
	
