		<div class="courseListDescription">This course surveys the application of game engines for the creation of virtual environments both in a studio context and on screen. Students will be introduced to important issues relating to the experience of virtual spaces through evaluation of creative projects, products and related research. Students will learn to model and animate objects, create environments and terrains, design interactions, manage assets and rendering.</div>
	
	
