		<div class="courseListDescription">This course will introduce students to basic material practices and physical object production.  Students will gain the necessary skills to model, design and build physical entities.  Students will be introduced to a variety of fabricating techniques as well as a range of materials.  Projects will challenge students to work at a variety of scales and within several contexts.  Individual and group projects will require development of personal and team based production skills.</div>
	
	
