    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/media/RTA/934.html" title="RTA 934 - Virtual Identities and Communities" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">RTA 934</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Virtual Identities and Communities</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This survey course examines the role of virtual environments in reshaping early 21st century notions of identity, communities and organizations. Through research projects, students analyze how these practices have altered the nature of mainstream society and question the future of western culture.</div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListLength"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Weekly Contact: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">Lecture: 3 hrs. </span></div>
	
	
