    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/media/RTA/953.html" title="RTA 953 - Mobility and Mixed Reality" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">RTA 953</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Mobility and Mixed Reality</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This course engages with mobile technologies and their impact on new media art practice through a discussion of contemporary artworks as well as hands-on exercises. This course explores how mobile technologies and mixed reality blur the boundaries between physical and virtual spaces, redefining the relationship we have to interfaces and places. Emphasis will be placed on the production of new participatory experiences focused on physical or virtual locations, boundaries and topologies.</div>
	
	
