		<div class="courseListDescription">In this course students will be introduced to transmedia platforms and their application to the sport industry.  By way of lectures, case studies and in-class workshops, students will learn new modes of story-telling by maintaining the overall narrative through multiple outlets.  Social media, gamification techniques, digital media and other cross-platform destinations will be examined.  This course will also introduce students to the creation of sports games on multiple platforms.</div>
	
	
