		<div class="courseListDescription">This course builds on the content of RTA 235 - Sport Media and Programming. Students will develop their particular areas of interest and career development within the sport industry and grow in their capacity to recognize and respond creatively to opportunity, and initiate and manage change. The course will focus on long form storytelling presented on various media. The students will design and produce a multi-platform long form sports presentation, utilizing advanced concepts related to the sport media field.</div>
	
	
